 but it's tough to become distant by pretending to break up. 

36
00:02:10,330 --> 00:02:12,230
 So, do you regret it? 

37
00:02:12,230 --> 00:02:15,610
 How you stood up for me in front of the kids two years ago? 

38
00:02:16,460 --> 00:02:21,060
 Well, you know. What if you really fell in love with someone else? 

39
00:02:21,060 --> 00:02:23,010
 I don't regret it at all. 

40
00:02:23,010 --> 00:02:26,110
 It's friendship over love for me any day. 

41
00:02:26,810 --> 00:02:30,060
 Are you sure you just haven't found a person to love over your friends? 

42
00:02:30,060 --> 00:02:32,170
 Is that the case? 

43
