56
00:03:13,900 --> 00:03:16,270
 That's when I vowed. 

57
00:03:16,270 --> 00:03:21,620
 That I'll also protect my only friend, A Jeong, and my only family, Ji Han, 

58
00:03:21,620 --> 00:03:25,020
 in any moment in life. 

59
00:03:27,190 --> 00:03:31,680
