74
00:05:12,550 --> 00:05:14,600
Lee Ji Han.

75
00:05:15,790 --> 00:05:18,090
Lee Ji Han!

76
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:22,420
- We need to talk more— 
 - What should we talk about?

77
00:05:22,420 --> 00:05:25,130
Do we even have something to talk about or...

78
00:05:25,130 --> 00:05:28,560
- I mean... 
 - Do you have something more to tell me?

79
00:05:32,950 --> 00:05:34,960
To summarize,

80
00:05:36,530 --> 00:05:40,010
you knew Brother was gay from the beginning, and

81
00:05:40,010 --> 00:05:44,640
your marriage was a fake one to hide his secret.

82
00:05:44,640 --> 00:05:47,680
And you hid that from me to the end, Na A Jeong.

83
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:50,030
I think we're done clarifying things.

84
00:05:50,030 --> 00:05:52,790
Is there anything I didn't comprehend here?

85
00:05:53,950 --> 00:05:56,540
Lee Ji Han, I also...

86
00:05:56,540 --> 00:06:00,020
- I also had my reasons— 
 - You should've told me sooner if you were going to.

87
00:06:00,020 --> 00:06:02,620
Just when were you going to tell me?

88
00:06:02,620 --> 00:06:06,090
How much of a pathetic fool did you want to turn me into?

89
00:06:08,850 --> 00:06:14,830
When we promised to stop hiding our feelings and putting up an act at the beach,

90
00:06:14,830 --> 00:06:17,220
was that all a lie?

91
00:06:20,340 --> 00:06:24,010
- That's not it— 
 - When did you tell Brother?

92
00:06:26,060 --> 00:06:31,370
The day I begged you to trust me and wait?

93
00:06:37,150 --> 00:06:39,940
It would've been better if that was the case.

94
00:06:41,410 --> 00:06:43,960
