108
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:54,250
Do Han.

109
00:07:54,250 --> 00:07:58,290
If you sincerely think of me as a friend, you can...

110
00:07:58,290 --> 00:08:00,790
You can reconsider your decision at least once.

111
