Why is Son-in-law here?

129
00:09:07,500 --> 00:09:11,420
You should at least eat before you go. The table's all set up.

130
00:09:11,420 --> 00:09:13,700
No, it's okay, Mother. I came without notice.

131
00:09:13,700 --> 00:09:16,310
Please invite me for a meal next time.

132
00:09:16,310 --> 00:09:18,540
Okay, then.

133
00:09:18,540 --> 00:09:23,380
Are you two coming home late today?

134
