Oh, yes. There are a lot of things to prepare.

135
00:09:26,500 --> 00:09:30,320
We need to look into a home, appliances, furniture, this and that.

136
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:31,920
That's true.

137
00:09:31,920 --> 00:09:35,480
I'm sorry I've been too busy with the wedding coming up and couldn't give you attention.

138
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:37,940
Gosh, not at all.

139
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:47,100
- I'll be back. 
 - Okay.

140
