144
00:10:00,970 --> 00:10:02,930
My gosh! Okay, then.

145
00:10:02,930 --> 00:10:04,560
- I'll get going. 
 - Yes, yes.

146
00:10:04,560 --> 00:10:06,240
Yes.

147
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:09,500
- Please take care. 
 - Yes, have fun!

148
00:10:18,540 --> 00:10:20,020
I'm sorry.

149
00:10:20,020 --> 00:10:22,280
Huh? For what?

150
00:10:23,040 --> 00:10:25,560
I couldn't really tell you properly yesterday—

151
00:10:25,560 --> 00:10:27,120
Oh, right. About our starter home.

152
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:28,860
It'd be better to get one in this neighborhood, right?

153
00:10:28,860 --> 00:10:31,420
It'll be close to your family, too.

154
00:10:32,170 --> 00:10:34,430
- Do Han. 
 - And about signing the marriage papers—

155
00:10:34,430 --> 00:10:36,370
Lee Do Han!

156
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:49,500
I'm also trying my best. Can't you see?

157
00:10:49,500 --> 00:10:51,380
I can see it.

158
00:10:52,270 --> 00:10:54,570
That's why it hurts even more.

159
00:10:59,780 --> 00:11:02,500
I'm sorry I couldn't keep my promise.

160
00:11:02,500 --> 00:11:04,330
I'm really sorry.

161
00:11:04,330 --> 00:11:07,270
I tried not to come this far.

162
00:11:08,150 --> 00:11:12,710
I was going to hold myself back somehow, but I failed.

163
00:11:12,710 --> 00:11:16,380
I think I like Lee Ji Han too much to do that.

164
00:11:16,380 --> 00:11:18,630
Do Han.

165
00:11:18,630 --> 00:11:20,730
I know I sound really insane

166
00:11:20,730 --> 00:11:23,740
and I know it's shameless of me to say this

167
00:11:23,740 --> 00:11:26,950
but can't you give me some slack just this once?

168
00:11:30,740 --> 00:11:35,320
If you continue to come off like this, I can't help it, either.

169
00:11:36,610 --> 00:11:38,590
Let's go to New York.

170
00:11:38,590 --> 00:11:40,540
- What? 
 - Forget the wedding and everything.

171
00:11:40,540 --> 00:11:43,100
We'll go to New York right away as we first planned.

172
00:11:43,100 --> 00:11:44,230
H-How could you—

173
00:11:44,230 --> 00:11:46,080
How could you do this to me?

174
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:49,740
Don't you know how I felt when I asked you to fake our marriage?

175
00:11:49,740 --> 00:11:52,000
I was really desperate, A Jeong.

176
00:11:52,000 --> 00:11:57,430
I wanted to hide my secret and create any breathing room I could, but—

177
00:12:00,440 --> 00:12:03,900
It's not like getting found out will only put me in trouble.

178
00:12:04,600 --> 00:12:08,640
Are you okay with your parents finding out, huh?

179
00:12:08,640 --> 00:12:11,830
Isn't that why you couldn't say anything earlier, either?

180
00:12:12,820 --> 00:12:15,370
I'm going this far to ask—

181
00:12:20,680 --> 00:12:22,970
Never mind, Do Han.

182
00:12:25,460 --> 00:12:28,020
It's natural for you to be like this.

183
00:12:29,820 --> 00:12:32,170
I'll make it up to you...

184
00:12:32,970 --> 00:12:35,540
for how I've wronged you somehow.

185
00:12:36,410 --> 00:12:39,320
But I can't do this anymore, either.

