You knew how I decided to go to you.

201
00:14:13,590 --> 00:14:17,410
You knew everything I gave up to go to you.

202
00:14:17,410 --> 00:14:22,220
I chose you over my brother, whom I thought was my everything in life, but...

203
00:14:22,220 --> 00:14:24,900
But you didn't feel quite the same.

204
00:14:24,900 --> 00:14:29,000
At first, it was Brother. And later, it was you, Na A Jeong.

205
00:14:30,370 --> 00:14:33,140
Do you know how I feel whenever it happens?

206
00:14:34,270 --> 00:14:37,290
As much as I risked my everything,

207
00:14:37,290 --> 00:14:40,440
it felt like my entire being was rejected.

208
00:14:42,390 --> 00:14:44,470
It's scary.

209
00:14:45,800 --> 00:14:50,600
I don't know what secret I'll find out now and how I'll be hurt again.

210
00:14:51,480 --> 00:14:54,530
Lee Ji Han, are you okay with us just—

211
00:14:54,530 --> 00:14:57,060
I'll have to get back now.

212
00:15:07,420 --> 00:15:10,930
How can he do that?

213
00:15:10,930 --> 00:15:14,080
How can he?

214
00:15:14,080 --> 00:15:16,390
I told you to leave for the day.

215
00:15:16,390 --> 00:15:20,200
Come on, how can I go anywhere without you, Ji Ae?

216
00:15:20,200 --> 00:15:22,780
But why are you so pretty?

217
00:15:22,780 --> 00:15:25,540
Still, you must be tired from work.

218
00:15:25,540 --> 00:15:28,780
What if it affects you tomorrow at work?

219
00:15:28,780 --> 00:15:32,460
Ji Ae, you're my top priority over everything.

220
00:15:32,460 --> 00:15:35,350
Gosh, you're so cool!

221
00:15:35,350 --> 00:15:38,210
You're so cool!

222
00:15:38,210 --> 00:15:42,810
How can half of a conversation be made up of "gosh"?

223
00:15:49,840 --> 00:15:52,390
By the way, Unni, is something wrong?

224
00:15:52,390 --> 00:15:55,140
You're not saying anything after seeing that.

225
00:15:55,930 --> 00:15:57,490
- Jong Hee. 
 - Yes?

226
00:15:57,490 --> 00:15:59,220
Do you want to go grab a drink today?

227
00:15:59,220 --> 00:16:02,860
I don't think I feel too good today—

228
00:16:13,380 --> 00:16:15,100
Yes. Hello?

229
00:16:15,100 --> 00:16:17,330
 This is Yoon Chae Won. 

230
00:16:17,330 --> 00:16:21,910
O-Oh, yes. Hello.

231
00:16:26,670 --> 00:16:28,900
You really came.

232
00:16:28,900 --> 00:16:31,080
Well, yes.

233
00:16:34,410 --> 00:16:36,700
I heard from Ji Han.

234
00:16:36,700 --> 00:16:39,440
He said he likes you, A Jeong.

235
00:16:43,020 --> 00:16:46,620
I hate becoming a part of a trashy drama like this,

236
00:16:46,620 --> 00:16:49,710
so I was going to forget about Ji Han.

237
00:16:49,710 --> 00:16:52,490
But it didn't really work.

238
00:16:52,490 --> 00:16:55,380
That's why I came. To clarify things.

239
00:16:56,610 --> 00:17:00,670
Do you feel the same way as Ji Han, A Jeong?

240
00:17:02,190 --> 00:17:03,690
Yes.

241
00:17:03,690 --> 00:17:06,000
Stopping you won't work?

242
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:07,740
Yes.

243
00:17:10,190 --> 00:17:13,480
You didn't even hesitate once, ever so shamelessly.

244
00:17:13,480 --> 00:17:16,570
I guess that's why things ended up this way.

245
00:17:18,530 --> 00:17:20,740
It's because I cherish Lee Ji Han that much.

246
00:17:20,740 --> 00:17:22,440
What about Do Han?

247
00:17:22,440 --> 00:17:24,630
Didn't you used to cherish Do Han at one point, too?

248
00:17:24,630 --> 00:17:28,610
Do Han... I still cherish him.

249
00:17:29,790 --> 00:17:32,930
I'm going to do anything to protect him.

250
00:17:32,930 --> 00:17:34,800
What?

251
00:17:34,800 --> 00:17:40,900
I'm really sorry, but I'm not in the best mood today. So, I'll take a shot first.

252
00:17:58,700 --> 00:18:00,590
What's this?

253
00:18:00,590 --> 00:18:03,620
So, you've lost contact with Ji Han right now?

254
00:18:03,620 --> 00:18:05,750
No, no.

255
00:18:06,340 --> 00:18:10,750
I keep hitting him up, but Lee Ji Han won't.

256
00:18:11,740 --> 00:18:14,570
But it's not a big deal.

257
00:18:15,630 --> 00:18:19,070
He's just a bit offish, I guess?

258
00:18:19,070 --> 00:18:23,000
It's just that he's a bit cold to me.

259
00:18:23,000 --> 00:18:28,860
Wait, I shouldn't have come here. I should've gone to Ji Han, huh?

260
00:18:28,860 --> 00:18:31,300
Why would you go there?

